query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_agendamentos,
  SUM(CASE WHEN paciente_nome IS NOT NULL AND paciente_nome != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as com_nome,
  SUM(CASE WHEN cpf_paciente IS NOT NULL AND cpf_paciente != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as com_cpf,
  SUM(CASE WHEN paciente_id IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as ja_vinculados
FROM agendamentos
WHERE importado_de = 'google_calendar';
